The complete syntax for adding an image on a page is:<br>
<tt>[[Image:{image_name}|{options}]]</tt> or <tt>[[File:{image_name}|{options}]]</tt> <br> 
The option entry may be omitted or one may enter one or a combination of any of the following options which are to be separated by pipes e.g. ''border'', ''left'', ''right'', ''center'', ''{width} px'' etc.
