If You want to change the logo of mediawiki.<br>
'''1.''' Go to your <tt>Localsettings.php</tt> file.<br>
'''2.''' Open your file in a texteditor and search for the variable <tt>$wgLogo</tt>.<br>
'''3.''' Now replace the value with the path to your logo. <br>
<pre>$wgLogo = $wgScriptPath."/skins/ontoskin3/logo.png";</pre><br>


