If you want to create a gallery with thumbnails you should: 

*Use the <code><nowiki><gallery></nowiki></code> tag.

The syntax that is to be used is: 
<pre>&lt;gallery&gt;
Image:{filename}|{caption}
Image:{filename}|{caption}
{...}
&lt;/gallery&gt;
</pre> 
Captions are optional and they may contain wiki links or other formatting. 

