If you wish to limit the number of search results that display, should select a '''type''' for your article.i.e.Category, Template, Image, PDF etc. 

To do this simply '''click''' on the article type in the '''''Refine Search''''' box above the search results. 

The result list changes accordingly and this time it will only display the results that belong to the selected article type. 
