'''Proposals for annotation ''' appear as green plus icon.
*When you '''click '''the green plus icon , the annotation dialog for properties pops up. It lets you enter the property's name in the usual menner. *Proceed to click on '''Add''' if all entries are valid. The proposal highlight will now be replaced with the annotation highlight. *If you want to '''cancel''' to property annotation just '''click'''&nbsp;''beside the input'' dialog or '''press''' the ''ESC'' key.
