Semantic Forms are very popular, since they enable you to easily enter data in SMW, but creating Semantic Forms for an (imported) ontology can be time-consuming and updates of the ontology require updates of related Semantic Forms.<br>
'''Automatic Semantic Forms''' Extension Provides automatically created Semantic Form to the 
Semantic Forms Extension  based on the Wiki ontology if no appropriate manually created Semantic Forms exist and facilitates information from build-in properties like ‚Has type‘ and ‚Has domain and range‘.
