There are DF tags in LocalSettings.php for an extension which does not exist or which at least does not have a deploy descriptor.<br>
'''Solution'''<br>
<tt>Remove the DF tags from LocalSettings.php or install a version of this extension which uses a deploy descriptor.</tt>

