The AdminSettings.php is missing. It is required for all scripts working on maintenance level including the [Deployment Framework]. It contains the database credentials.<br>
'''Solution'''<br>
<tt>There is a template shipped with Mediawiki which must simply be modified: AdminSettings.template</tt>
 $wgDBadminuser      = 'root';
 $wgDBadminpassword  = 'm8nix';
<tt>Add your credentials and save the file as: AdminSettings.php </tt>

