This error occurs when there are extensions installed which lacks other extensions. The reason is either the dependant extension is not installed at all or it has the wrong version.<br> Note that only extensions compatible with the Deployment Framework do have a formal description of what other extensions they require.<br>
'''Solution'''<br>
*<tt>Check which extension is missing and download the appropriate version within the given range.</tt><br>
*<tt>Download the SemanticMediawiki (latest possible version) deployable from [http://sourceforge.net/projects/halo-extension/ sourceforge]</tt>

