The Ontology Browser displays all the consistency issues that the Consistency bot identifies. If a page has gardening issues, the title is displayed in orange and a '''warning triangle''' displays next to it. 

If a category is in orange and it does not have a warning triangle this indicates that this'''category''' has direct or indirect issues in its instances, or direct or inherited issues in its properties. 
