The '''Gardening Log''' special page is used just like the Wiki-Query pages: *You can browse through the pages with '''next/previous''' buttons. *You can change the number of issues displayed per page.
Behind each issue, is a little icon which can be clicked to '''expand'' and view the detailed information about a gardening issue. There is also a button at the bottom of the page which lets you '''expand/collapse''' all issues at once.
