These features are hosted in the toolbox that is labeled as '''Property Properties'''. 

The properties of a property are:

#'''Domain'''&nbsp; 
#'''Range'''&nbsp; 
#'''Inverse of'''&nbsp; 
#'''Type''' 
#'''Minimal cardinality'''&nbsp; 
#'''Maximum cardinality'''&nbsp; 
#'''Transitivity''' 
#'''Symmetry'''


