The similarity bot is used to find redundant entities in the wiki. It may be accessed from the Gardening interface. 

It has 4 parameters (all are optional): 

# '''Similarity term''': Searches for entities similar to the given term. If left empty, all entities are compared to each other thereby looking for redundant terms . 
# '''Lexical similarity''': This is a factor which indicates the degree of lexical similarity. 
# '''Limit of results''': Maximum number of results.&nbsp; 
# '''Filtering of results''': Shows only results which at least have a given rating.&nbsp;

{{Copyright of article
