The system requirements are the same as for the Halo extension and can be found at the [http://smwforum.ontoprise.com/smwforum/index.php/Download Download page]. It's recommened to use MediaWiki 1.15 and PHP 5.2.x on the server side and Firefox 3.x or Internet Explorer 8 on the client side.
